#. <html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><meta content="Pali text from the Mahāsaṅgīti Tipiṭaka Buddhavasse 2500" name="description"><title></title></head><body><div id="text" lang="pli"><section class="sutta" id="pli-tv-bu-vb-np12"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs0.1"
msgid "Theravāda Vinaya"
msgstr "Theravāda Collection on Monastic Law"

#. </p><p class="division"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs0.2"
msgid "Mahāvibhaṅga"
msgstr "Monks’ rules and their analysis"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs0.3"
msgid "Nissaggiyakaṇḍa"
msgstr "The chapter on relinquishment"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs0.4"
msgid "Kosiyavagga"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs0.5"
msgid ""
msgstr "Monks’ Relinquishment"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs0.6"
msgid "12. Suddhakāḷakasikkhāpada"
msgstr "12. The training rule on entirely black"

#. </h1></div><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Origin story"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-np.12.1"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.2.74"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="2109"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.1"
msgid ""
"Tena samayena buddho bhagavā vesāliyaṃ viharati mahāvane kūṭāgārasālāyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying at Vesālī in the hall with the peaked "
"roof in the Great Wood."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena chabbaggiyā bhikkhū suddhakāḷakānaṃ eḷakalomānaṃ "
"santhataṃ kārāpenti."
msgstr ""
"At that time the monks from the group of six were getting blankets made "
"entirely of black wool."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.3"
msgid ""
"Manussā vihāracārikaṃ āhiṇḍantā passitvā ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "People who were touring the dwellings grumbled and complained,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.4"
msgid ""
"“kathañhi nāma samaṇā sakyaputtiyā suddhakāḷakānaṃ eḷakalomānaṃ santhataṃ "
"kārāpessanti, seyyathāpi gihī kāmabhogino”ti."
msgstr ""
"“How can the Sakyan ascetics get blankets made entirely of black wool, just "
"like lay people who indulge in sensual pleasures?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="2110"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.5"
msgid ""
"Assosuṃ kho bhikkhū tesaṃ manussānaṃ ujjhāyantānaṃ khiyyantānaṃ vipācentānaṃ."
msgstr "The monks heard the complaints of those people,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.6"
msgid "Ye te bhikkhū appicchā … pe …"
msgstr "and the monks of few desires …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.7"
msgid "te ujjhāyanti khiyyanti vipācenti—"
msgstr "complained and criticized those monks,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.8"
msgid ""
"“kathañhi nāma chabbaggiyā bhikkhū suddhakāḷakānaṃ eḷakalomānaṃ santhataṃ "
"kārāpessantī”ti."
msgstr ""
"“How can the monks from the group of six get blankets made entirely of black "
"wool?”"

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="2111"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.9"
msgid ""
"Atha kho te bhikkhū chabbaggiye bhikkhū anekapariyāyena vigarahitvā "
"bhagavato etamatthaṃ ārocesuṃ … pe …"
msgstr "After criticizing those monks in many ways, they told the Master. …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.10"
msgid ""
"“saccaṃ kira tumhe, bhikkhave, suddhakāḷakānaṃ eḷakalomānaṃ santhataṃ "
"kārāpethā”ti?"
msgstr "“Is it true, monks, that you do this?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.11"
msgid "“Saccaṃ, bhagavā”ti."
msgstr "“It’s true, Master.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.12"
msgid "Vigarahi buddho bhagavā … pe …"
msgstr "The Buddha rebuked them, “…"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.13"
msgid ""
"kathañhi nāma tumhe, moghapurisā, suddhakāḷakānaṃ eḷakalomānaṃ santhataṃ "
"kārāpessatha."
msgstr "Foolish men, how can you get blankets made entirely of black wool?"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.14"
msgid "Netaṃ, moghapurisā, appasannānaṃ vā pasādāya … pe …"
msgstr "This will not give rise to confidence in those without it …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.15"
msgid "evañca pana, bhikkhave, imaṃ sikkhāpadaṃ uddiseyyātha—"
msgstr "And, monks, this training rule should be recited thus:"

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.15a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Final ruling"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="4"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="2112"></a>
#. <span class="rule"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.16"
msgid ""
"“Yo pana bhikkhu suddhakāḷakānaṃ eḷakalomānaṃ santhataṃ kārāpeyya, "
"nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyan”ti."
msgstr ""
"‘If a monk gets a blanket made entirely of black wool, he commits an offense "
"entailing relinquishment and confession.’”"

#. </span> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs1.17"
msgid "(<em>12</em>:<strong>31</strong>)"
msgstr ""

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.0a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Definitions"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="5"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-np.12.2"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.2.75"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="2113"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.1"
msgid "Yo panāti"
msgstr "A:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.2"
msgid "yo yādiso … pe …"
msgstr "whoever … "

#. </span><span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.3"
msgid "bhikkhūti"
msgstr "Monk:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.4"
msgid "… pe …"
msgstr ""
"… The monk who has been given the full ordination by a complete Order "
"through a procedure consisting of one motion and three announcements that is "
"unchallengeable and fit to stand—"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.5"
msgid "ayaṃ imasmiṃ atthe adhippeto bhikkhūti."
msgstr "this sort of monk is meant in this case."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="6"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="2114"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.6"
msgid "Kāḷakaṃ nāma"
msgstr "Black:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.7"
msgid "dve kāḷakāni—"
msgstr "there are two kinds of black:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.8"
msgid "jātiyā kāḷakaṃ vā rajanakāḷakaṃ vā."
msgstr "natural black and dyed black."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="7"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="2115"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.9"
msgid "Santhataṃ nāma"
msgstr "A blanket:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.10"
msgid "santharitvā kataṃ hoti avāyimaṃ."
msgstr "it is made by spreading out, not by weaving."

#. </span></p><p><a class="sc" id="8"></a><a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.226"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="2116"></a>
#. <span class="term"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.11"
msgid "Kārāpeyyāti"
msgstr "Gets made:"

#. </span><span class="gloss"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.12"
msgid "karoti vā kārāpeti vā, payoge dukkaṭaṃ."
msgstr ""
"for the act of making the blanket, or getting it made, he commits an offense "
"of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.13"
msgid "Paṭilābhena nissaggiyaṃ hoti."
msgstr "When he gets the blanket, it becomes subject to relinquishment."

#. </span></p><hr><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.14"
msgid "Nissajjitabbaṃ saṃghassa vā gaṇassa vā puggalassa vā."
msgstr ""
"The blanket should be relinquished to an Order, a group, or an individual."

#. <span class="kamma"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.15"
msgid "Evañca pana, bhikkhave, nissajjitabbaṃ …"
msgstr "“And, monks, it should be relinquished in this way. …"

#. <span class="pe"> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.16"
msgid "pe …"
msgstr ""
"To be expanded as in <a class=\"cr\" href=\"./pli-tv-bu-vb-np1#13\">"
"Relinquishment 1, paragraphs 13–17</a>, with appropriate substitutions. …"

#. </span> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.17"
msgid ""
"“idaṃ me, bhante, suddhakāḷakānaṃ eḷakalomānaṃ santhataṃ kārāpitaṃ "
"nissaggiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"‘Venerables, this blanket which I got made entirely of black wool is to be "
"relinquished."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.18"
msgid "Imāhaṃ saṃghassa nissajjāmī”ti … pe …"
msgstr "I relinquish it to the Order.’ …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.19"
msgid "dadeyyāti … pe …"
msgstr "the Order should give …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.20"
msgid "dadeyyunti … pe …"
msgstr "you should give …"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.21"
msgid "āyasmato dammīti."
msgstr "‘I give this blanket back to you.’”"

#. </span></p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.21a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Permutations"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="9"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="2117"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.22"
msgid "Attanā vippakataṃ attanā pariyosāpeti, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"If he finishes what he began himself, he commits an offense entailing "
"relinquishment and confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.23"
msgid "Attanā vippakataṃ parehi pariyosāpeti, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"If he gets others to finish what he began himself, he commits an offense "
"entailing relinquishment and confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.24"
msgid "Parehi vippakataṃ attanā pariyosāpeti, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"If he finishes himself what was begun by others, he commits an offense "
"entailing relinquishment and confession."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.25"
msgid "Parehi vippakataṃ parehi pariyosāpeti, nissaggiyaṃ pācittiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
"If he gets others to finish what was begun by others, he commits an offense "
"entailing relinquishment and confession."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="10"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="2118"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.26"
msgid "Aññassatthāya karoti vā kārāpeti vā, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If he makes one, or gets one made, for someone else, he commits an offense "
"of wrong conduct."

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.27"
msgid "Aññena kataṃ paṭilabhitvā paribhuñjati, āpatti dukkaṭassa."
msgstr ""
"If he obtains one that was made by someone else and then uses it, he commits "
"an offense of wrong conduct."

#. </p><h2>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.27a"
msgid ""
msgstr "Non-offenses"

#. </h2><p><a class="sc" id="11"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="2119"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.28"
msgid "Anāpatti—"
msgstr "There is no offense:"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.29"
msgid ""
"vitānaṃ vā bhūmattharaṇaṃ vā sāṇipākāraṃ vā bhisiṃ vā bibbohanaṃ vā karoti,"
msgstr ""
"if he makes a canopy, a floor cover, a screen-wall, a mattress, or a pillow;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.30"
msgid "ummattakassa,"
msgstr "if he is insane;"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.31"
msgid "ādikammikassāti."
msgstr "if he is the first offender."

#. </p><hr><p class="endsutta"><a class="sc" id="12"></a><a class="wt-pa" id="2120"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-np12:pts-cs2.32"
msgid "Suddhakāḷakasikkhāpadaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ dutiyaṃ."
msgstr "The second rule, the training rule on entirely black, is finished."

